PN,42502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1779012401
OL,3,CSuspended Reform councillor apologises
OL,4,Cfor alleged racist social media post
OL,6,FIssuing an apology, Mr Gibbins said:
OL,7,F"A number of years ago, prior to
OL,8,Fstanding for election and before
OL,9,Fjoining Reform UK, I made a series of
OL,10,Fposts on my personal Facebook profile
OL,11,Fwhich were intended as jokes, but were
OL,12,Fmade in extremely poor taste and with
OL,13,Fpoor judgement.
OL,15,F"I fully recognise that these comments
OL,16,Fwere entirely inappropriate and I
OL,17,Fsincerely apologise to anyone who may
OL,18,Fhave been offended by them. The posts
OL,19,Fdo not reflect my personal beliefs or
OL,20,Fvalues, and I regret both the language
OL,21,Fused and the offence caused.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
