PN,42503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1779012401
OL,3,CSuspended Reform councillor apologises
OL,4,Cfor alleged racist social media post
OL,6,F"My focus is fully on serving the
OL,7,Fresidents who elected me, and I remain
OL,8,Fcommitted to representing the people
OL,9,Fof Hylton Castle Ward to the best of
OL,10,Fmy ability."
OL,12,FOn Monday evening (11 May), a Reform
OL,13,Fspokesperson said Mr Gibbins had been
OL,14,Fsuspended from the party pending an
OL,15,Finvestigation.
OL,17,FHe will now represent the Hylton
OL,18,FCastle ward as an independent.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/4
